extends layout

block content
    .page.js-page
      // One Page Sidebar
      .one-page-sidebar
        // One Page Sidebar Header
        .one-page-sidebar-header
          // One Page Logo
          .one-page-logo
            // Logo Image
            a.logo-image(href='/hr_managers')
              img(src='/images/logo2.png')
            br
            a.logo-image(href='/hr_managers')
              img(src='/images/manager.png')
        .one-page-nav-wrapper.js-custom-scrollbar
          ul.one-page-nav.js-one-page-nav(data-prepend-to='.js-prepend-mobile-menu')
            li.is-active
              a(href='#what')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-question
                | What is purpose of the recruiters?
            li
              a(href='#add_recruiter')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-user-plus
                | Add Recruiter
            li
              a(href='#search_recruiter')
                span.one-page-search
                  i.fa.fa-search
                | Search Recruiter
            li
              a(href='#assign_team')
                span.one-page-icon
                  i.fa.fa-cubes
                | Assign Team
            li
              a(href='#admin_access')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-user
                | Admin access
            li
              a(href='#resend_credentials')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-send
                | Resend credentials
            li
              a(href='#delete_recruiter ')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-trash
                | Delete Recruiter
            li
              a(href='#suspend_recruiter')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-ban
                | Suspend Recruiter
        // End of One Page Nav
        // One Page Sidebar Footer
        footer.one-page-sidebar-footer
          | All Rights Reserved.
          a(href='http://www.masymbol.com/', target='_blank') Masymbol Technologies
          |  Pvt Ltd © 2016
        // End of One Page Sidebar Footer
      // End of One Page Sidebar
      // One Page Content
      .one-page-content
        // Header
        header.header.large.header-one-page.js-header-fixed
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .row
              .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-5
                .visible-sm-block.visible-xs-block
                  // Logo Image
                  a.logo-image(href='/')
                    img.img-responsive(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/skilledtree-public/logo.png', alt='logo')
                  // End of Logo Image
              .col-md-9.col-sm-6.col-xs-7
                // Menu
                nav.right.helper
                  ul.menu.sf-menu.js-menu
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers')
                        i.fa.fa-home.fa-lg
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/introduction')
                        | Introduction
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/team') Team
                    li
                      a.active(href='#') Members
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/employees') Employees
                        li
                          a.active(href='/hr_managers/recruiter') Recruiter
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/manager') Manager
                    li
                      a(href='#') Jobs
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/Jobs') Jobs
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/resumes') Resumes
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/gamification') Gamification
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/reports') Reports
                    li
                      a(href='#') Branding
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/career') Career Page
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/companybrand') Company Branding
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/dashboard') Dashboard
                    li
                      a(href='#') Header
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/header') Header Icons
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/settings') Settings
                // End of Menu
        // End of Header
        #content
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #what.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1 What is purpose of the recruiters?
                p.category-content
                  | As you know that each team has multiple recruiters. These recruiters are going to handle your company recruitment activities. Each recruiter is responsible to complete the recruitment activities once after the resumes gets uploaded by the employees in SkilledTree.
                  br
                  | Recruiter can only see the assigned team jobs and its corresponded resumes and also he/she can post the jobs. He/She is the person who will schedule the interview and change the resume status of the applied candidates.
            .col-md-12
              #add_recruiter.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Add Recruiter
                p.category-content
                  | Before adding recruiters, Make sure that you have added ‘Team’ in the ‘Settings’ section. ‘Default’ team is added when you create your organization account in SkilledTree. Name, Email/Phone and Team can be added by the HR Manager in the ‘Management’ section. One or more recruiters can be added at a single time by clicking ‘Add more’ button. If the recruiter has Email Id, Login credentials will be sent to his/her email client. SMS will be sent to recruiters if you entered their phone number.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/addrecruiter.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              #search_recruiter.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Search Recruiter
                p.category-content
                  | You can search the recruiter by entering their email in the search box given there in ‘Recruiter’ under Management section.
            .col-md-12
              #assign_team.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Assign Team
                p.category-content
                  | If you want to move a recruiter from one team to another team, this can be possible by clicking the editable dropdown in the Recruiter's List which is right below on ‘Recruiter’ section.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/teamrecruiter.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              #admin_access.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1 Admin access
                p.category-content
                  | HR Admin can perform all the functionality such as adding recruiters, managers, employees, team and posting jobs etc., In order to make recruiter as admin, give admin access by enabling the button ‘Give Admin Access’ in the Recruiter’s List. HR Admin Access can be revoked by clicking the same button again.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #resend_credentials.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Resend credentials
                p.category-content
                  | You can send login credentials to the recruiter,  if the recruiter has not yet joined SkilledTree or not yet received the credentials. He/She will be receiving either an Email or  SMS.
            .col-md-12
              #delete_recruiter.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Delete Recruiter
                p.category-content
                  | Recruiters will be deleted from the database when he/she resigned the job in your organization or can be deleted by manually.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #suspend_recruiter.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Suspend Recruiter
                p.category-content
                  | Recruiters can be suspended by clicking the ban icon in the list.
    // End of One Page Content
